<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cancellation Warning - Engagematic</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdcb6e 0%, #e17055 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .warning-box {
            background-color: #fff9e6;
            border-left: 4px solid #fdcb6e;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .warning-box h3 {
            color: #d63031;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .value-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .value-box h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Cancellation Scheduled</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi <%= name || 'there' %>,</h2>

            <p>We noticed you've scheduled your subscription cancellation. Your subscription will end on <strong><%= cancellationDate || 'the end of your billing period' %></strong>.</p>

            <div class="warning-box">
                <h3>What This Means</h3>
                <p>After <%= cancellationDate || 'your billing period ends' %>, you'll lose access to:</p>
                <ul style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.8;">
                    <li>Premium content generation features</li>
                    <li>Advanced analytics and insights</li>
                    <li>Priority support</li>
                    <li>Unlimited usage</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px;"><strong>Good news:</strong> All your content and data will be preserved!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value-box">
                <h3>Before You Go...</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 18px; margin: 15px 0;">You've created <strong><%= postsCount || '0' %> posts</strong> and generated <strong><%= engagementCount || '0' %> engagements</strong> with Engagematic!</p>
                <p style="opacity: 0.9;">That's amazing progress. Are you sure you want to stop now?</p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>We're here to help:</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Need help with a specific feature? We can provide a personal walkthrough</li>
                <li>Facing any issues? Our support team is ready to assist</li>
                <li>Looking for a different plan? We can find the perfect fit for you</li>
            </ul>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= keepSubscriptionUrl %>" class="cta-button">
                    Keep My Subscription â†’
                </a>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you've already made up your mind, no worries! We respect your decision and you can always come back anytime.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If there's anything we can do to change your mind, just reply to this email. We're here to help!</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br><strong>The Engagematic Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Engagematic. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

